description: Irish Foreign Affairs Minister Simon Coveney says more north-south co-operation is needed.
title: Coronavirus: More north-south co-operation needed on Covid-19, Coveney says
title_page: Coronavirus: More north-south co-operation needed on Covid-19, Coveney says - BBC News
maintext: "I'd like to speak to some of the senior politicians in Northern Ireland today to establish exactly what is the blockage there because certainly was very clear with me yesterday that funding should not be the blockage," he added.
